overview:
Mission: To combine style and effectiveness by creating an innovative new energy band design with unique color combinations. To promote health and well-being by making negative ion therapy bands available to every consumer around the world.

Products: Mad Panda, LLC specializes in the designing and manufacturing of energy bracelets. These are silicone bands which contain precious metals that have been found to enhance energy and that promote positive health in numerous ways. We have had customers report health benefits who suffer from arthritis, insomnia, and pain during physical therapy.
